http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Industries-celebrate-Republic-Day/article14022578.ece

Republic Day was celebrated by various industries in the city with patriotic fervour and a pledge administered among the employees to increase productivity and ensure cost-effectiveness.Several industries also took the occasion to give awards to senior employees in recognition of their contribution to the organisation. Cultural programmes preceded by ceremonial parades marked the celebrations.Worker hoists flagThe highlight of celebrations by BHEL (Heavy Plate and Vessels Plant) was the unfurling of the tricolour by senior worker G. Malla Rao. The plant gives the opportunity to a senior worker every year.Executive Director J. Sankaran was the chief guest.